raaz : reboot is a 2016 indian supernatural thriller film written and directed by vikram bhatt . the film stars emraan hashmi and kriti kharbanda in the lead roles . the film is produced by mukesh bhatt and mukesh bhatt under the banners of vishesh films . the film features emraan hashmi and kriti kharbanda in pivotal roles . the film is scheduled to be released on 16 july 2016 .